n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[搵工要小心，切勿中美容教育傳銷陷阱]  大學生小心職場陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164225%2Fpage%2F1&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8XlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=c1964449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8XlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=c283d234\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b302d2ebf8948b657ad72aca9e7a00a48a751364","tid":2083130,"uid":347934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T20:54:44.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n朋友我大把"},{"pid":"9aa74287e120696e7b59bc5e6a8163a8166a4c0e","tid":2083130,"uid":320048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T20:54:59.000Z","msg":"24"},{"pid":"d1aedc68ace47